Patterns for nixcpp deps (since there are a lot of these).
The cover only builds in nix-from-scratch/pkgs, on the way to nixcpp build in nix-from-scratch/pkgs/nix/

no-build (binary install)                stage1-linux-headers, mdbook, mdbook-linkcheck
configure_exec override                  boost (bootstrap.sh), nlohmann_json (cmake)
extra configure args                     python
in-source build                          unzip, nix, zstd
custom cppflags                          sqlite
non-trivial patch                        libssh2, m4, cmake
full custom install                      stage1-linux-headers
non-trivial post-install script          pkgconf, bzip2
